| Light | White FFFFFF | Black 000000 | Green 008000 | Blue 0000FF | Red A31515 | Green 09885A |
| Dark | Black 000000 | White D4D4D4 | Green 608B4E **_Insufficient Contrast!!**_ | Blue 569CD6 | Red CE9178 | Green B5CEA8 |

